name: CryptoJunky
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crypto junky
des:
Unlike other cryptocurrency skills, with this skill you can get the latest prices for any cryptocurrency listed on binance.com. This includes Litecoin, Bitcoin, and dozens of other cryptocurrencies! The prices are in US Dollars for now. For example you can get the latest prices for:

Bitcoin
Litecoin
Verge
Tron

and so forth!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
